<div type="definition">
<p>CAUSE TO BECOME MORE GOOD.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for changing something for the better is gǎi 改.</p>
<p>2. Fù 復 is to improve something so as to restore it to its original shape.</p></div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
